          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "威风凛凛坐梁山，盖世英雄非等闲。除暴安良本夙愿，不与奸佞共一天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，及时雨宋江。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "智多星吴用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "公孙胜",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "入云龙公孙胜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前者攻打祝、扈二庄，那贼累次抗拒义兵，至堪痛恨。闻得时迁被擒，不知生"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "死，为此点动大兵，前去攻打二庄，搭救时迁上山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先生，请来传令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "石秀听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "石秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你扮作樵夫模样，探听祝家庄不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "石秀",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（石秀下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨林听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你扮作募化道人模样，暗地保护石秀，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨林",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨林下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "杨雄听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨雄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你解压粮草，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "杨雄",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（杨雄下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王英听令！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命你攻打扈家庄，不得有误！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴用",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿此去旗开得胜，"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦明、花荣、李逵、黄信",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马到成功！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，攻打扈家庄去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦明、花荣、李逵、黄信",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
