    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "李逵"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走哇！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（李逵上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "豪杰生来多任性，"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诚心扶保宋公明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，黑旋风李逵。只因宋大哥带领人马下山，攻打扈家庄。众家弟兄分路攻打"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去了，就不差俺李二。啊呵有了！俺只好私自下山，倘遇机会，俺就杀他个落"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "花流水。看天色尚早，就此走遭也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不遵将令下山林，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
