    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "宋江",
        "秦明",
        "花荣",
        "黄信"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖牌子〗。四龙套、秦明、花荣、黄信、宋江同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "前道为何不行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "秦明、花荣、黄信",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来到扈家庄。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人马列开！"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，且住！看此庄深沟高垒，甚是严密。树木层层，好一村庄也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "宋江",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将官，扎下营盘！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
