    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四女兵",
        "扈三娘",
        "报子",
        "王英"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扈三娘上，起霸。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扈三娘 （醉花阴） 披挂整齐，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凤翅飞耀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "百忙里炮似轰雷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也顾不得临阵前万敌施威。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫他血染战袍回。"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴家，一丈青扈三娘。正在花园游玩，忽听庄丁来报，梁山宋江，带领一干毛"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼前来骚扰我庄，为此全身披挂提防御敌。贼子啊贼子！这才是太岁头上动土。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔，众女兵！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四女兵、四下手、大旗同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四女兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随你姑娘出庄观阵者！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喜迁莺） 俺只见旌旗蔽日，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王英上，上高台。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王英下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喜迁莺） 猛听得鼍鼓声雷，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凭怎生双翅飞出重围。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王英讨战！"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众女兵，带马！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（喜迁莺） 我提画戟管叫他人头落地，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，怎能知俺勇冠无敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
