    {
      "scene_index": 6,
      "label": "第六场",
      "characters_present": [
        "扈三娘",
        "王英"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四女兵、四下手、大旗、扈三娘同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扈三娘 （刮地风） 哎呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺可也气吐虹霓。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四上手、王英同上，同会阵。四女兵、四下手、大旗、四上手同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个娇婆娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个矮汉子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！扈三娘，闻得你武艺高强，今日见了你王爷，敢么是怯战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "住了！看你身体不满三尺，敢与你姑娘交战？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一丈青，你休嫌我身量矮小，有道是：泰山高遮不住太阳，秤砣小能压千斤。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我若战你不过，情愿与你做……"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "做一个女婿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸，贼子！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刮地风） 我笑，笑着他毛贼无见识，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎知俺枪法无敌？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一霎时将贼擒提。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扈三娘下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咦啊，想我战她不过，怎么她倒败了？啊呵是了！想是她心中有了我了，待俺"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "紧紧地赶上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！扈三娘休走，王爷赶来了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（王英追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "王英→扈三娘",
          "turns": 4
        },
        {
          "edge": "扈三娘→王英",
          "turns": 4
        }
      ],
