        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听人喊马嘶，待某登高一望。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、秦明、花荣、黄信、宋江同上，过场，同下。四下手、四女兵同上，过场，同下。扈三娘上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个黑汉子！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个娇婆娘！"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！这一黑汉，为何挡住奴家的去路？"
        },
        {
          "character": "李逵",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你李逵爷爷在此。这一斧，劈你两半！"
        },
        {
          "character": "扈三娘",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看枪！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扈三娘、李逵同开打，扈三娘、李逵同下。）"
